My grandfather was in Merrill’s Marauders in WW2.  He got Malaria.  Suffered from it off and on for the remainder of his life.  A Malaria vaccine is the amazing realization of dreams of many for decades.   

Something doesn’t happen very often, and this is Something.

What a wonderful piece of good news today!
